{"id": "1184397875627692122", "channel_id": "1184397875627692122", "type": 0, "author_id": "1184389155636133921", "author_name": "emersonpoe", "author_bot": false, "content": "游戏内容方面，就我想到的话，新活动新剧情新角色的发布是按照什么样的时间间隔呢？pvp和pve的后续开发会相对侧重哪个方面呢？\n游戏系统方面，pve不知道官方有没有考虑过好友助战之类的东西？", "timestamp": "2023-12-13T07:34:18.598000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184397875627692122", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」官方有什么能够稍微透露的开发方向嘛？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
